                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The American Treaty on Pacific Settlement (Pact of Bogotá) was not sent to the
                    Senate for advice and consent to ratification and so did not enter into force
                    for the United States. It was ratified by Mexico on November 23, 1948, and by
                    Costa Rica on May 6, 1949, and was subsequently ratified by a number of other
                    countries for whom it thus entered into force.</p>
            </div>
